%% Diagram: Rsc Flight Stream Sequence
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant E as Edge\n(SSR + RSC)
    participant DB as Database

    B->>E: 1. GET /products
    E->>E: 2. Render server tree
    E->>DB: 3. Query products
    DB-->>E: 4. Rows
    E-->>B: 5. Shell + first chunks
    Note over E,B: Stream continues as\nSuspense boundaries resolve
    E->>DB: 6. Query reviews\n(suspended)
    DB-->>E: 7. Rows
    E-->>B: 8. Flight chunk\n(reviews subtree)
    B->>B: 9. Patch DOM placeholder
    B->>B: 10. Hydrate client islands
    Note over B: Server code never\ncrosses the wire
